items.title: Hamas urges Israel to halt strikes on Gaza City as it searches for two hostages
items.standfirst: Hamas lost contact with two of the Israeli hostages the group was holding during intensified Israeli strikes in Gaza City over the past two days, its armed wing said on Sunday. The al-Qassam Brigades called on Israel to halt air strikes for 24 hours starting at 6pm local time as it tries to locate the missing hostages.
